<i>noun</i>: 폭풍우 [폭풍우], 비바람 [비바람] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭풍우 [폭풍우]</dt><br>
<dd>1. rainstorm</dd><br>
<dd>폭풍이 불면서 세차게 쏟아지는 비.</dd><br>
<dd>Rain pouring strongly in a storm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hardship</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 생활이나 사업에서 고통이나 어려움을 겪음.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) One’s state of going through trouble or difficulty in life or in business.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비바람 [비바람]</dt><br>
<dd>1. rain and wind</dd><br>
<dd>비와 바람.</dd><br>
<dd>A compound noun meaning the rain and wind.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rainstorm</dd><br>
<dd>세차게 내리는 비와 함께 강하게 부는 바람.</dd><br>
<dd>A strong wind blowing along with a heavy rain.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>